data.description: Port Orange Pool Home! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom pool home is your opportunity to live the Port Orange lifestyle at a price you can afford!This home offers an incredible opportunity to create your dream space. While it may need some updates, the potential is endless. With a little imagination and a vision, you can transform this house into your perfect oasis and unleash your creativity and transform this backyard into your personal paradise! The home features new windows that fill every room with natural light. The split floor plan offers privacy and convenience, with the living room, family room, and dining room providing ample space for all your family's needs Located in the desirable community of Sweetwater Hills in Port Orange, this home is conveniently situated near top rated schools, shopping, dining, and our beautiful beaches. Don't miss out on this chance to make this house your own and bring your unique style to life. Contact us today to schedule a showing and start envisioning the possibilities!
